{
  "info": {
    "name": "Kickoff API",
    "description": "API manajemen tim sepak bola — Go/Gin/GORM + JWT Auth\n\n## Setup\n1. Jalankan aplikasi (lokal atau Docker)\n2. Kirim request **Auth > Login** menggunakan kredensial seed\n3. Token JWT otomatis tersimpan ke variable `jwtToken`\n4. Gunakan request di folder lain (semua sudah menyertakan header Authorization)\n\n## Seed Data Default\n| Role | Email | Password |\n|---|---|---|\n| ADMIN | admin@xyz-football.local | ChangeMe123! |\n| MANAGER | manager@xyz-football.local | ChangeMe123! |\n| USER | user@xyz-football.local | ChangeMe123! |\n\n**Team IDs:** Jakarta Mavericks=1, Bali Dragon=2, Bandung Giants=3\n**Player IDs:** 1-12 (4 per tim)\n**Match ID:** 1 (FINISHED), 2-3 (SCHEDULED)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "kickoff"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/health",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["health"]
            },
            "description": "Cek status server (public, no auth required)"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "OK",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json; charset=utf-8" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"status\": \"ok\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "description": "Endpoint publik untuk mengecek status server"
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login — Admin",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@xyz-football.local\",\n  \"password\": \"ChangeMe123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login sebagai ADMIN. Token JWT otomatis tersimpan ke variable `jwtToken`."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"jwtToken\", jsonData.token);",
                  "    console.log(\"Token tersimpan: \" + jsonData.token.substring(0, 50) + \"...\");",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Login Berhasil (200)",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json; charset=utf-8" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n  \"user\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"name\": \"Default Admin\",\n    \"email\": \"admin@xyz-football.local\",\n    \"role\": \"ADMIN\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Login Gagal (401)",
              "status": "Unauthorized",
              "code": 401,
              "header": [
                { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json; charset=utf-8" }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"error\": \"invalid email or password\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login — Manager",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"manager@xyz-football.local\",\n  \"password\": \"ChangeMe123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login sebagai MANAGER (mengelola Tim ID=1). Token JWT otomatis tersimpan."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"jwtToken\", jsonData.token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login — User",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@xyz-football.local\",\n  \"password\": \"ChangeMe123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login sebagai USER (read-only, tidak bisa manage apapun)."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"jwtToken\", jsonData.token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "description": "Autentikasi — dapatkan JWT token untuk mengakses API"
    },
